data.description: Old World Florida Charm in the middle of the City!!  The majestic oak trees surround this 1925 home situated on over 3/4 of an acre more or less corner lot.  With 4 bedrooms in the main house and an additional 1 bedroom 1 bath mother in law suite/apartment in the basement this home is ready for its next generation.  The property has a large detached 2 car garage and 2 car carport. The main home features a large screened front porch and a 1 car attached carport.  The current owners have enjoyed this home for more than 5 decades and the family has owned it for even longer.  Sellers require a lease of the basement apartment for $1,000 per month.
